<item>
            <title>[MGPG-9] gpg plugin hangs when it should prompt for the secret key passphrase hangs</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MGPG-9</link>
                <project id="12317521" key="MGPG">Maven GPG Plugin (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When used in conjunction with the release plugin the release:perform command hangs when it should prompt for the secret key passphrase.  Interestingly enough when I put the passphrase into the settings.xml file the plugin does not hang.  I suspect the prompt is failing to show up.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Maven 2.0.6, JDK 1.5.0_11, Linux 2.6.x</environment>
        <key id="12803310">MGPG-9</key>
            <summary>gpg plugin hangs when it should prompt for the secret key passphrase hangs</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
